subject: THIS IS THE NEW PAYMENT ARRA
body:
THIS IS THE NEW PAYMENT ARRANGEMENT
This is to notify you that your fund are currently being lodged into
wood forest bank in USA because we held meeting today with the
(FBI)which they totally gives beneficiaries like you the opportunity
to transfer fund via telephone banking to be able to escape IMF
against transfer of fund above 1million US dollars .
This new payment arrangement is designed to help you get access to
global telephone banking and complete transfer of fund without any
delay.Reconfirm your full name,address,occupation,your mobile phone
and your ID , this is to make sure you are the right person

subject: Re:   THIS IS THE NEW PAYMENT ARRA
body:
Dear James Lew,

Thank you for your email. I am interested in the new payment method you mentioned, but I need more information about it. Could you please provide more details about how this telephone banking system works? 

Also, could you clarify what you mean by "escape IMF against transfer of fund above US dollars"? I'm not sure I understand this part.

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Audrey
